def _cython_agg_blocks(
    self, how: str, alt=None, numeric_only: bool = True, min_count: int = -1
) -> "Tuple[List[Block], Index]":
    data: BlockManager = self._get_data_to_aggregate()

    if numeric_only:
        data = data.get_numeric_data(copy=False)

    if data._is_view and alt is not None and how not in {"ohlc", "median"}:
        data = data.copy()

    agg_blocks: List[Block] = []
    new_items: List[np.ndarray] = []

    for block in data.blocks:
        agg_values, mutated_items = self._cython_agg_block(
            block, how, numeric_only=numeric_only, min_count=min_count
        )
        agg_block = block.make_block(agg_values, placement=block.mgr_locs)

        new_items.append(mutated_items)
        agg_blocks.append(agg_block)

    # Combine everything and then glue what we can
    agg_blocks, agg_items = BlockManager._assemble_from_blocks(agg_blocks, axes=[data.items])
    blocks = _extend_blocks(agg_blocks, new_items)

    return blocks, agg_items
